Morixels Mega Colab #2 is the Second and one of the biggest Collaborations that happen on the FXHash and also in the NFT Community.

In this Collaboration, 24 artists plus I, have designed their artwork as pixel art. Each artist has 5 Artworks in this collection, which have been randomly combined with Borders that I designed (Morteza Yousefi, idea owner and art director)
I designed the borders in such a way that by combining them, we find Unique borders that can be minimal or complex, or abstract.

This combination has got a beautiful effect in a random way, and besides that, this collection is very valuable because of the reputation and Ideas of the 25 artists and the Collaboration of 25 Artists.

The number of Traits in this collection is 7 (176 layers) and it has the ability to make 60,963,840 unique NFTs.

To create balance, these NFTs are randomly minted, and this is a chance for everyone to get a rare version. So due to the low price of these NFTs, if the rare version did not belong to you, it is still possible for you to mint the new NFTs.

To Produce this collection, all the layers were designed pixel by pixel, which was time-consuming and difficult. And this greatly increases the value of this collection.

